  EffectDiscription_ENG: "\uFF1CBlocker\uFF1E (When an opponent's Digimon attacks,
    you may suspend this Digimon to force the opponent to attack it instead.) [On
    Deletion] If it's your opponent's turn, reveal the top 3 cards of your deck.
    Add 1 black card among them to the hand. Place the rest at the bottom of the
    deck in any order."
